"" frameborder=\""0\"" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen style=\""background: black\""><\/iframe>\n        "",""captions"":[]},""url"":""https:\/\/www.udemy.com\/mobile-app-design-from-scratch\/"",""numInvitationRequests"":null,""isPublished"":""Yes"",""isInAppPurchaseEnabled"":true,""isGoogleInAppPurchaseEnabled"":true,""favoriteTime"":false,""archiveTime"":false,""googleInAppPurchasePriceText"":""$24"",""inAppPurchasePriceText"":""$23.99"",""isAvaliableOnIos"":true,""hasCertificate"":true,""locale"":""en_US"",""status"":""published"",""description"":""<p>  \t<em>\u201cDesign is not just what it looks like and feels like. Design is how it works.&quot;<\/em> - Steve Jobs.<br>  \t<br>  \t   This course is not just about creating a pretty app, it\u2019s about designing an app that works great and happens to be beautiful. Working at least 30 minutes a day, you can complete this course in 2 weeks, which develops the workflow needed to turn your idea into a fully designed product.  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong> Learn to Design Engaging Apps With This Beginners Mobile App Design Course <\/strong><br>  <\/p>  <ul>  \t<li>User Experience Research and Design<\/li>  \t<li>Outlining Visual Concept <\/li>  \t<li>Designing the First Version<\/li>  \t<li>Redesigning Our App<\/li>  \t<li>Creating a Style Guide<\/li>  <\/ul>  <p>  \t<strong> User Experience and App Development <\/strong><br>  \t   In 2008, apps designed for tablets and smartphones began appearing in app distribution platforms, operated by the owners of the mobile operating systems. It\u2019s important for mobile application developers to consider things like screen sizes and hardware specifications when creating a mobile app. The user interface (UI) design is an essential part of mobile app creation and considerable time should be taken to consider creating a valuable user experience (UX).  <\/p>  <p>  \t   Apps are in high demand and developers are producing applications for multiple services and businesses, including GPS location-based services, banking, games, medical, and more. With the large number of Apps available, review websites have been created in order to make discovering apps easier. For this reason it\u2019s important to put a lot of time into designing your UX.  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong> Contents and Overview <\/strong><br>  \t   With 30 lectures, over 7 hours of material, you will to develop a workflow for your idea, find the right way to build your app, and understand how to use the design principles. <br>  <\/p>  <p>  \t   This course begins by teaching you what UX is and how it affects the UI design. You\u2019ll begin creating mockups and visual concepts for your idea. Next, you\u2019ll begin designing the first version of your app and learning how to preview it on a device. Following the first design of your application, you\u2019ll work on redesigning the navigation, home content, and camera flow. Once you have completed the redesign of your application, you will learn how to design an icon for the app and showcase your finished app design.  <\/p>  <p>  \t   After completing this course you\u2019ll be able to create an engaging mobile app design from start to finish, no previous experience is needed to learn the UI design principles. This course will benefit entrepreneurs, developers, and designers looking to move into the mobile applications market.  <\/p>  <p>  \t*** You need to have a Mac to take this course ***  <\/p>""},{""__class"":""course"",""id"":""121372"",""title"":""How to Trade Stock Options: Profiting in Up and Down Markets"",""headline"":""How to earn 30% or more on your money each year. This proven options blueprint gives you an accelerated path to riches."",""numLectures"":148,""numSubscribers"":443,""contentInfo"":""37 hours"",""originalPriceText"":""$895"",""numOfReviews"":51,""numOfTextReviews"":37,""avgRating"":4.6863,""avgRatingRounded"":4.7,""price"":""895"",""owner"":{""__class"":""user"",""id"":""2152218"",""title"":""Travis Wilkerson"",""jobTitle"":""Lead Stock Option Trader; OPF Success Academy"",""description"":""<p>  \t            Travis Wilkerson (AKA Trader Travis) is the lead stock option trader and founder of the Option Profit Formula Success Academy. He has published well over $3,000 of free information through his website Learn Stock Options Trading dot com.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            Travis invested in stocks and mutual funds, with minimal success before he learned about stock options. He has now been trading options on a full time basis since early 2004. Initially he was motivated to learn about options trading because he was in the middle of a real estate business failure.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            One of Travis&#039;s friends introduced him to someone whom he believed could help. He was a multi-millionaire and had been trading stock options for 20+ years. The first thing he did was teach Travis some basic budgeting skills so that he would not end up in the same financial mess years later.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            As the lessons progressed his mentor eventually taught him about stock options and how to trade them successfully. The experience proved to be invaluable. Within three months he had tripled his account size.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            In an enlightened and egotistical state of mind Travis thought he was a natural born pro and made a typical amateur mistake\u2026<strong>He started betting his entire account on one trade at a time trying to get rich faster.<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t            And it worked!  <\/p>  <p>  \t            For about two years, and then his habits caught up with him. He crashed and burned and had to start all over.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            A valuable lesson was learned. Having a great deal of head knowledge about stock options doesn&#039;t necessarily mean you&#039;ll be a great trader.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            Broken and humiliated Travis took a few years off from trading. He eventually went back to the basics and started all over again, this time giving up on the idea of getting rich quick.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            The change in attitude made all the difference, he&#039;s had continued success since then!  <\/p>  <p>  \t         After the Bear Market of 2007-2009 Travis <strong>tripled his retirement account<\/strong> and recorded video proof so that he can show his students the strategy he used (Buy and Manage Secrets Training).  <\/p>  <p>  \t         And since then, <strong>Travis has consistently earned 30-50% on his money each year<\/strong> by trading options. And he records his trading in real time to show his students what full time trading looks like (Trade School Training).  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong>Travis knows what works and what doesn&#039;t work and you get to benefit from his mistakes by avoiding them.<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t            And you can thank his wife for his website as well as his training programs. She got tired of him talking her head off about investing so she encouraged him to create a website about trading and that in turn became a hugely popular coaching program.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            All in all Travis is just a down to earth regular guy who loves helping people and believes that every good thing is meant to be shared.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            I hope you enjoy the valuable training he has decided to share with you.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            God Bless...  <\/p>"",""url"":""https:\/\/www.udemy.com\/u\/traviswilkerson\/"",""images"":{""img_50x50"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/50x50\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_75x75"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/75x75\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_100x100"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/100x100\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_125_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/125_H\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_200_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/200_H\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg""}},""images"":{""img_50x50"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/50x