progressed his mentor eventually taught him about stock options and how to trade them successfully. The experience proved to be invaluable. Within three months he had tripled his account size.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            In an enlightened and egotistical state of mind Travis thought he was a natural born pro and made a typical amateur mistake\u2026<strong>He started betting his entire account on one trade at a time trying to get rich faster.<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t            And it worked!  <\/p>  <p>  \t            For about two years, and then his habits caught up with him. He crashed and burned and had to start all over.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            A valuable lesson was learned. Having a great deal of head knowledge about stock options doesn&#039;t necessarily mean you&#039;ll be a great trader.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            Broken and humiliated Travis took a few years off from trading. He eventually went back to the basics and started all over again, this time giving up on the idea of getting rich quick.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            The change in attitude made all the difference, he&#039;s had continued success since then!  <\/p>  <p>  \t         After the Bear Market of 2007-2009 Travis <strong>tripled his retirement account<\/strong> and recorded video proof so that he can show his students the strategy he used (Buy and Manage Secrets Training).  <\/p>  <p>  \t         And since then, <strong>Travis has consistently earned 30-50% on his money each year<\/strong> by trading options. And he records his trading in real time to show his students what full time trading looks like (Trade School Training).  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong>Travis knows what works and what doesn&#039;t work and you get to benefit from his mistakes by avoiding them.<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t            And you can thank his wife for his website as well as his training programs. She got tired of him talking her head off about investing so she encouraged him to create a website about trading and that in turn became a hugely popular coaching program.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            All in all Travis is just a down to earth regular guy who loves helping people and believes that every good thing is meant to be shared.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            I hope you enjoy the valuable training he has decided to share with you.  <\/p>  <p>  \t            God Bless...  <\/p>"",""url"":""https:\/\/www.udemy.com\/u\/traviswilkerson\/"",""images"":{""img_50x50"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/50x50\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_75x75"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/75x75\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_100x100"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/100x100\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_125_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/125_H\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg"",""img_200_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/200_H\/2152218_cae6_2.jpg""}}],""instructionalLevel"":""Appropriate For All"",""promoAsset"":{""__class"":""asset"",""id"":""784986"",""type"":""Video"",""title"":""Promo Video"",""contextInfo"":""02:57"",""streamUrl"":""https:\/\/dabm6vlh6a177.cloudfront.net\/2013-11-19_17-36-51-49484d0893128b3facd0c2a396db58dd\/WebHD.mp4?Expires=1412507197&Signature=c28PG3jCYWRVM~jcKQohZqX-ck8CDQbUd0GlZsNhdcjI~xyXDeX-ERr5DuDk151DMrwbgkLlvJrF2zDWuTTlVl3pEcWBOD-yBFuJb9watt8NXfPWyE63x7VrARU3ZKS4d41s5GfrAa7bHb6K6uuuQUTROJJYgNbIW3m2jJltalHOPhxbqKghmWVJKpNpZs4PJVYa12jLnd2jou84l0B1YIUUjCt9sjrvrt5MvrzPZNb93~y2d1xbFkrttbQ1bwwAOjTY5~v62wDLyKP5euomGH-bLc44gHy8OEGEO1lsD9l4IYnlSlSZM1BjHtjbPXTKfd8gprwdWBWsZwcwpnCNHg__&Key-Pair-Id=APKAI7LVCUGIDCBBVTCQ"",""downloadUrl"":{""Video"":[""https:\/\/dabm6vlh6a177.cloudfront.net\/2013-11-19_17-36-51-49484d0893128b3facd0c2a396db58dd\/WebHD_720p.mp4?response-content-disposition=attachment%3Bfilename%3Dpromo-video.mp4&Expires=1412507197&Signature=krckiUBdsl2Ti31JHhAjocG8CGvRKFXxj~4bHvOI2drKocE61wnwX7CKELnXTga39I-WOjkbmmGzeke7fSoHAJpkhrICip9b9OGgyxY7wlqT~HNHJH8uWfLkRQ0WIVdOVNz4IBKRVEj~la8YkiHuoQYlFRJebRCoIUoBNeCfz8