os"":true,""hasCertificate"":true,""locale"":""en_US"",""status"":""published"",""description"":""<p>  \t<strong>Earn 2 vital certifications for one low price -- AND beat the January 30, 2015 CCNP exam deadline, guaranteed!<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t            I Guarantee You&#039;ll Pass All Three CCNP Exams Before The January 29, 2015 Deadline, Or You Get Updated Course 100% Free!  <\/p>  <p>  \t            Plus....  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong>In October, join my CCNP All-In-One Video Boot Camp, and you get full access to my CCNA Security Video Boot Camp absolutely FREE!<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong>Just email your receipt to success@thebryantadvantage.com and we&#039;ll set you up!<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong>We&#039;re also donating 100 meals to the Central Virginia FoodBank for every signup in October!<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t<strong>Only purchases made in October are eligible for the free course.  Thanks!<\/strong>  <\/p>  <p>  \t              Over 60,000 students in my Video Boot Camps have made me the #1 instructor on Udemy, and now it&#039;s your turn to earn your CCNP -- with a little help from yours truly!  <\/p>  <p>  \t                   You receive full access to all 50+ hours of the course, including downloading - you can download one video or download them all!   You&#039;ll have permanent online access to watch the videos whenever you like as well, and there&#039;s a Q&amp;A forum right here on Udemy where you can post questions - and I&#039;ll answer them personally!  <\/p>  <p>  \t                 The videos are in order -- CCNP SWITCH, ROUTE, and TSHOOT - and clearly labeled, so you know EXACTLY what to watch for each exam.  <\/p>  <p>  \t                   From my unbeatable methods of mastering BGP all the way through tough OSPF and EIGRP route redistribution scenarios, you&#039;ll see it all right here on LIVE Cisco routers and switches - and you can watch every single session as often as you like.  <\/p>  <p>  \t                   Thanks for making The Bryant Advantage part of your CCNP success story!  <\/p>  <p>  \t                   Chris Bryant<br>  \t                    CCIE #12933  <\/p>  <p>  \t                   &quot;The Computer Certification Bulldog&quot;  <\/p>""},{""__class"":""course"",""id"":""117652"",""title"":""The $400k Crowdfunding Launch Formula"",""headline"":""Learn how I raised over $400k (now over $500k as of 3\/15\/14) using online marketing hacks for crowdfunding raises."",""numLectures"":59,""numSubscribers"":4904,""contentInfo"":""5 hours"",""originalPriceText"":""$999"",""numOfReviews"":81,""numOfTextReviews"":76,""avgRating"":4.8395,""avgRatingRounded"":4.8,""price"":""999"",""owner"":{""__class"":""user"",""id"":""248706"",""title"":""Eli Regalado"",""jobTitle"":""Chief of Madness at Mad Hatter Agency"",""description"":""<p>  \tEli Regalado is a serial entrepreneur. He&#039;s the founder and Chief of Madness at Mad Hatter Agency (because he couldn&#039;t hold down a respectable job).  Mad Hatter specializes in growth hacking and operates out of the Innovation Pavilion in Centennial CO.  <\/p>  <p>  \tEli sees crowdfunding as the future and is positioning his company to be a thought leader in the space of taking innovative companies to market via the crowd. In the last 12 months he&#039;s successfully led his team to crowdfund over $400k on various crowdfunding platforms.  <\/p>  <p>  \tBig on building social capital for his clients, Eli has personally met and worked with some of the greatest minds on the planet including Apple Founder Steve Wozniak, Wikipedia Founder Jimmy Wales, Internet Inventors Larry Roberts and Vint Cerf, 8 Latin American Presidents, and many many more.  He has a degree from Hard Knocks University on Social Engineering and a Masters in The Art Of The Hustle.  <\/p>  <p>  \tAll of his tactics are self taught, practical, and drip of common sense.  A lost art form in today&#039;s business world.  <\/p>  <p>  \tEli also started a grassroots political movement (even though he does not vote) with two other friends that boasts over 450k Facebook fans and has been featured on the Washington Post, Fox, CNN, and other politically charged and seldom correct media outlets.  <\/p>  <p>  \tEli has ADHD, 6 sisters, 2 kids, a motorcycle, and a strong unquenchable desire to create and innovate.  He loves collaborating and stalking people on Facebook, Linkedin, and Twitter.  <\/p>  <p>  \tWatch out. You could be next.  <\/p>"",""url"":""https:\/\/www.udemy.com\/u\/eliregalado\/"",""images"":{""img_50x50"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/50x50\/248706_9109_4.jpg"",""img_75x75"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/75x75\/248706_9109_4.jpg"",""img_100x100"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/100x100\/248706_9109_4.jpg"",""img_125_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/125_H\/248706_9109_4.jpg"",""img_200_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/user\/200_H\/248706_9109_4.jpg""}},""images"":{""img_50x50"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/50x50\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_75x75"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/75x75\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_100x100"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/100x100\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_125_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/125_H\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_200_H"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/200_H\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_480x270"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/480x270\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_304x171"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/304x171\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_240x135"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/240x135\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_96x54"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/96x54\/117652_76dd_5.jpg"",""img_48x27"":""https:\/\/dujk9xa5fr1wz.cloudfront.net\/course\/48x27\/117652_76dd_5.jpg""},""isPaid"":true,""visibleInstructors"":[{""__class"":""user"",""id"":""